{"tid":440206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯去信促查戴耀廷　要求港大2周內回覆","createTime":"2017-10-18T14:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T16:22:16.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc1cdeffcad85eab12049c33ed3e176d6a1493c8","tid":440206,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:08:15.000Z","msg":"身為律師的立法會議員何君堯今(18日)去信香港大學校務委員會主席李國章，並把副本抄送至港大校長馬斐森，要求港大於14日內回覆是否對佔中發起人、港大法律系副教授戴耀廷啟動正式調查程序，以及作出停職留薪的安排。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯於信中指，自己於上月13日去信馬斐森，要求對方澄清是否已正式接受他於8月24日投訴戴耀廷行為失當一事，並展開調查程序，但基於馬斐森至今仍未就此事作出回應，他今天去信港大校委會，再次批評戴耀廷於2013年開始鼓吹佔中等違法行動，又指戴正被檢控，憂慮對方在教學上繼續宣揚「公民抗命」、「違法達義」等歪念誤導學生及青年，就此，他要求港大交代是否對戴耀廷啟動正式調查及停職留薪安排，並載列包括戴耀廷副教授擾亂社會秩序時序表等3個附件供有關方面參考。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171018/bkn-20171018212733897-1018_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171018%2Fbkn-20171018212733897-1018_00822_001.html&d=eHgTl0akRFSu%2Bkp8QTI6lqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=7a548c15\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171018/bkn-20171018212733897-1018_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"05636d1603da8ae89feb449a31ee39754aedcd49","tid":440206,"uid":10100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"仲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a394a602978dab3ca17a838adaae3e82824d179","tid":440206,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢殺無赦都仲未搞掂佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f86d04d230ee8e7370298b